trans-unit.source: Passed to custom WSDL exporters and importers to enable customization of the metadata export and import processes for a WSDL endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Har överförts till den anpassade WSDL exportörer och importers för att aktivera anpassning av metadata exportera och importera processer för en WSDL-slutpunkt.

trans-unit.source: The WsdlEndpointConversionContext class represents the context in which the custom WSDL for an endpoint is either exported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> or imported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WsdlEndpointConversionContext representerar kontexten där anpassade WSDL för en slutpunkt är antingen exporteras med <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>eller importeras med hjälp av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The following properties enable you to retrieve the WSDL document object model for the current WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> for the endpoint contract.
trans-unit.target: Följande egenskaper gör att du kan hämta WSDL document object model för den aktuella WSDL: – <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>egenskapen hämtar den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName>för slutpunktskontraktet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>Egenskapen hämtar den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName>för den aktuella slutpunkten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A> property gets the binding for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>Egenskapen hämtar bindningen för den aktuella slutpunkten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A> property gets the port for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>Egenskapen hämtar porten för den aktuella slutpunkten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>

trans-unit.source: - - The following methods enable you to add or remove custom WSDL elements to the appropriate scopes in the exported or imported WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A> method returns the fault binding for the specified fault.
trans-unit.target: --Följande metoder kan du lägga till eller ta bort anpassade WSDL-objekt till lämpliga omfattningar i den exporterade eller importerade WSDL: – <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>metoden returnerar fel-bindning för den angivna feldomänen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A> method returns the fault for the specified fault binding.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>Metoden returnerar fel för den angivna fel-bindningen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A> method returns the message binding for the specified message.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>Metoden returnerar meddelandet bindningen för den angivna meddelandet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A> method returns the message for the specified message binding.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>Metoden returnerar meddelandet för den angivna bindningen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A> method returns the operation binding for the specified operation.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>Metoden returnerar åtgärdsbindning för den angivna åtgärden.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A> method returns the operation for the specified operation binding.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>Metoden returnerar åtgärden för den angivna åtgärdsbindningen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>
